content.raw:
Very helpful.  

When I incorporate the model, using Gazebo version 7.14.0, I get a bunch of new warnings…

    Warning [parser.cc:835] XML Element[inertia], child of element[link] not defined in SDF. Ignoring[inertia]. You may have an incorrect SDF file, or an sdformat version that doesn't support this element.

We’ll also probably want to include it in the tutorials, but we can take care of that on this end.
